title: War of the Roses: He Has Teeth Marks Where?!?
description: Lily got the weirdest call from a complete stranger saying that her fiance had slept with his wife.  She confronted her fiance, Braden, about it and he claims he isn't cheating but now Lily found something else that makes her think that he is.
